pull_request.title: build(deps-dev): bump black from 23.9.1 to 23.10.0
pull_request.body:
Bumps [black](https://github.com/psf/black) from 23.9.1 to 23.10.0.
Release notes

Sourced from black's releases.

23.10.0

Stable style

  • Fix comments getting removed from inside parenthesized strings (#3909)

Preview style

  • Fix long lines with power operators getting split before the line length (#3942)
  • Long type hints are now wrapped in parentheses and properly indented when split across multiple lines (#3899)
  • Magic trailing commas are now respected in return types. (#3916)
  • Require one empty line after module-level docstrings. (#3932)
  • Treat raw triple-quoted strings as docstrings (#3947)

Configuration

  • Fix cache versioning logic when BLACK_CACHE_DIR is set (#3937)

Parser

  • Fix bug where attributes named type were not acccepted inside match statements (#3950)
  • Add support for PEP 695 type aliases containing lambdas and other unusual expressions (#3949)

Output

  • Black no longer attempts to provide special errors for attempting to format Python 2 code (#3933)
  • Black will more consistently print stacktraces on internal errors in verbose mode (#3938)

Integrations

  • The action output displayed in the job summary is now wrapped in Markdown (#3914)
Changelog

Sourced from black's changelog.

23.10.0

Stable style

  • Fix comments getting removed from inside parenthesized strings (#3909)

Preview style

  • Fix long lines with power operators getting split before the line length (#3942)
  • Long type hints are now wrapped in parentheses and properly indented when split across multiple lines (#3899)
  • Magic trailing commas are now respected in return types. (#3916)
  • Require one empty line after module-level docstrings. (#3932)
  • Treat raw triple-quoted strings as docstrings (#3947)

Configuration

  • Fix cache versioning logic when BLACK_CACHE_DIR is set (#3937)

Parser

  • Fix bug where attributes named type were not acccepted inside match statements (#3950)
  • Add support for PEP 695 type aliases containing lambdas and other unusual expressions (#3949)

Output

  • Black no longer attempts to provide special errors for attempting to format Python 2 code (#3933)
  • Black will more consistently print stacktraces on internal errors in verbose mode (#3938)

Integrations

  • The action output displayed in the job summary is now wrapped in Markdown (#3914)

  • 9edba85 Prepare release 23.10.0 (#3951)
  • bb58807 Fix parser bug where "type" was misinterpreted as a keyword inside a match (#...
  • 722735d Fix grammar for type alias support (#3949)
  • abe57e3 Treat raw strings like other docstrings (#3947)
  • 1648ac5 Fix long lines with power operator(s) getting splitted before line length (#3...
  • 6f84f65 Migrate mypy config to pyproject.toml (#3936)
  • 3bb9214 CI Test: Deprecating 'Healthcheck.all()' from Hypothesis in fuzz.py (#3945)

issue.title: 简单部署
issue.body:
1.phpstudy 安装一个mysql 创建数据库djangosspanel
2.修改db.py文件

![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/b9d83a65-f4cb-4e5f-ad4a-b21147263a0b)
3.配置.env
![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/ace0e335-25bc-4bd8-8280-66bb904ac38e)
4.安装python
![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/a8bf98f1-0927-4c42-b344-24968f902de4)
5.克隆git clone https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel.git
 
![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/a10da926-1b0a-41b0-bb50-ee25d8af1756)
6.导入数据库python manage.py migrate
![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/41a01096-f231-426b-88b4-310d1cbc5ce0)
7.创建管理员信息python manage.py create_admin --email "admin@qq.com" --username "admin" --password "admin"
![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/ecd3f0ba-af89-4d2b-8450-83f86ce66171)
8.安装各种模块，根据提示去pip install 
9.运行服务python manage.py runserver

![image](https://github.com/Ehco1996/django-sspanel/assets/44092526/0690fc58-62bd-4601-946b-508fe98a41b7)

comment.body:
> > 欢迎将文档提到 doc 分支里形成文档 🙏
> > 另外当前的确不支持在后台直接创建用户，并不是 bug 哦
> 
> 管理员就无法修改用户的密码了

你这样说的确, 欢迎提供 pr

why do we need to set this manually?  it seems that `_gateway` is pravite var in the pkg `alipay.AliPay`

check the inner code
```python
        if debug:
            # self._gateway = "https://openapi.alipaydev.com/gateway.do"
            self._gateway = "https://openapi-sandbox.dl.alipaydev.com/gateway.do"
        else:
            self._gateway = "https://openapi.alipay.com/gateway.do"

```
